{"tid":230577,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"林敏驄嘆填詞人地位不再︰藝術家變工匠","createTime":"2017-05-05T12:40:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-06T08:24:01.000Z","uid":69737,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b0db2d1b7b0295c7b56df4bf9c63e3f588b2ef9d","tid":230577,"uid":69737,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T12:40:05.000Z","msg":"原文 <a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170505/s00007/1493969526158\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170505%2Fs00007%2F1493969526158&d=73P4J9mxZbud55ZbF8SGicP%2FddU7lKBqZb2OVh9Tir8%3D&h=8e467b4d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170505%2Fs00007%2F1493969526158&h=6dd6b8cc\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170505/s00007/1493969526158</a><br />\n<br />\n林敏驄經歷過兩次婚姻失敗，先後與李美鳳、陳伶俐離婚收場的他自嘲是「農務系研究生」，拒絕再婚，不會再為任何一棵樹而放棄整個森林﹗<br />\n<br />\n曾在80年代寫下無數經典情歌的他近年鮮有新作品，林敏驄解釋︰「寫了幾年歌詞就不再寫是因為無人唱﹗當年的歌手如張國榮、梅艷芳、譚詠麟均很有星味，他們走近你時，你會驚，現在的歌手太平民化了﹗」<br />\n<br />\n他也慨嘆現在的填詞人地位不再，常被人點來點去要求改歌詞。林敏驄說︰「<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>這不是藝術家，只是工匠﹗我就是權威，絕不改歌詞﹗你會否叫金庸改一段《書劍恩仇錄》？叫畢加索重畫畫作？瘋了嗎？</strong></span>」<br />\n<br />\n霸氣盡現！！！"},{"pid":"945c2e14c6a368cbe729a9896db3f9a6aa562b35","tid":230577,"uid":3122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T12:43:22.000Z","msg":"好波"},{"pid":"11db4f84a307507bc1a6bdab55582491b1397fe4","tid":230577,"uid":522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T12:55:03.000Z","msg":"無錢搵就無地位架啦，這就是香港"},{"pid":"07f06d0da524d70a6f3c65e9b7c8c39247dc6a55","tid":230577,"uid":39177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T12:58:00.000Z","msg":"勝了一仗,我負了修養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8da3124873eca7627d74a9eec318c1d1a1e0189e","tid":230577,"uid":29702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score